{"tid":2415621,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中国人又播毒】柬埔寨社區爆32例感染 全都是中国人！","createTime":"2021-02-20T11:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T04:38:13.000Z","uid":293677,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cdbb3ec04473ad622b5de5b1ed55ea456398320c","tid":2415621,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:39:34.000Z","msg":"2021/02/20 19:26<br />\n<br />\n〔中央社〕柬埔寨總理洪森（Hun Sen）今天說，境內一個中國人社區爆發武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情。此事讓原本堪稱順利的柬埔寨防疫工作破功。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">法新社報導，柬埔寨迄今控制疫情的表現頗佳，首都金邊的生活大致已回歸常軌。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但一群中國人為了取得赴海外旅行所需的醫療證書而接受病毒採檢，今天發現結果呈陽性反應，令人擔心社區疫情擴大。<br />\n<br />\n洪森在國營電視台播放的演說中表示：<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">「我們發現大型社區感染，共32起病例&hellip;這對我們來說是很糟的狀況。今天發現的陽性反應全都是中國人。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n這些病例出自一家夜店，目前已關閉。洪森說，政府正追蹤接觸史，看是否有其他人感染。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">柬埔寨各地出現愈來愈多中國商家，在部分柬埔寨人民之間引發漸趨高漲的反中情緒</span></strong>；洪森在電視演說中呼籲人民，不要因為這波社區感染就歧視中國人。<br />\n<br />\n柬埔寨上次出現本土病例是在去年11月。這個擁有超過1600萬人口的國家，迄今累計逾500起確診病例，無人病故。<br />\n<br />\n強人總理洪森是全球在位最久的領袖之一，累計掌權已35年，他向來是中國政府的堅定盟友，而柬埔寨收受中國數以十億計美元的軟貸款和投資。<br />\n<br />\n在疫情初期，許多國家對最早發現病例的中國關閉邊境，洪森卻不願跟進，甚至於去年2月親赴北京與中國國家主席習近平會面，展現兩國團結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3444546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3444546&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkpLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=b6d4d0e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3444546&h=44904df8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3444546</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"x-large\">變革中国 輸出病毒</span></span>"},{"pid":"be31d30389e21f6623c9ae4f937889ec2c92ef66","tid":2415621,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />變革中国 輸出病毒<br />\n<br />\n刁近平又贏<br />\n<br />\n各國繼續舔共話唔係病毒戰<br />\n<strong>有份舔共果D元首等同殺自己國民</strong>"},{"pid":"3865744d42b25cc743d906809648fd9b4fa38c4e","tid":2415621,"uid":103050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:54:25.000Z","msg":"柬埔寨正宗垃圾奶共國家<br />\n用支共手法對付支國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d36f815e9c315e53334079d89a55c466177611","tid":2415621,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:00:12.000Z","msg":"支那人=病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf06228f18ddef09f860a9d58fa96f565e6c8d5","tid":2415621,"uid":227628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:01:17.000Z","msg":"厲害了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae07192f4c483c7346181f5187d43e6e349579c","tid":2415621,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:02:28.000Z","msg":"支那人無打支那苗？"},{"pid":"624e5714b2c767a5d71ea6e191b4bcb5f4c64efb","tid":2415621,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:02:57.000Z","msg":"疫苗外交報捷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce5e6e14bd9426ce7fd8f74b6e3d609167a3eba","tid":2415621,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:20:52.000Z","msg":"食左誠實豆沙包呀<br />\n竟然唔屈美國人播毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4b813acd19917b45c481fc88c8b32dc625fcc3","tid":2415621,"uid":183058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:31:09.000Z","msg":"跳舞群組其實都係啲支那牛郎惹過嚟 <img src=\"/assets/fa